Katharine Willa Sipio

Music.
In my free time, I like to pretend that I'm a rockstar.


I currently run a rather goofy YouTube channel with my sister where we put up music covers of songs we like. I try to update it monthly with current jams the best I can — requests are always welcomed! Music is one of my true passions, and I love to write and perform songs. It's also incorporated into the majority of my digital projects somehow. I hope to put up some of my own original music on here in the near future, so please stay tuned. I also make mixtapes like they're going out of style and basically exchange them like they're currency. If you would like one, or would like to trade, feel free to contact me!
